mmit-2024-05-27/</link><description>朝鲜周一谴责中国、日本和韩国承诺实现朝鲜半岛无核化，称三国在首尔举行的罕见峰会后发表的联合声明是侵犯朝鲜主权的“严重政治挑衅”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-condemns-denuclearisation-discussion-south-korea-japan-china-summit-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>万科亏损底价出售深圳地块</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-sells-shenzhen-land-plot-loss-making-reserve-price-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一提交的一份文件显示，资金短缺的万科通过拍卖以人民币 22.4 亿元（约合 3.0918 亿美元）的价格出售了深圳一块地块，比近七年前购买同一块 19,000 平方米地块的价格低了 27% 以上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-sells-shenzhen-land-plot-loss-making-reserve-price-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织总干事谭德塞对最终达成大流行病条约“充满信心”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/who-chief-tedros-confident-eventual-pandemic-treaty-deal-2024-05-27/</link><description>世界卫生组织总干事周一表示，相信各国在上周未能达成协议后有一天能够就流行病协议达成协议，尽管卫生官员警告称这可能需要数年时间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 09:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/who-chief-tedros-confident-eventual-pandemic-treaty-deal-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、中国、日本四年来首次峰会后联合声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-joint-declaration-after-first-summit-four-years-2024-05-27/</link><description>韩国、中国和日本领导人周一发表联合声明，涵盖贸易、气候变化和老龄化社会等一系列领域的合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 08:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-china-japan-joint-declaration-after-first-summit-four-years-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾抗议中国年度禁渔令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-protests-chinas-annual-fishing-ban-2024-05-27/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周一表示，菲律宾抗议中国在南海单方面实施为期四个月的禁渔令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 07:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-protests-chinas-annual-fishing-ban-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴全球速卖通聘请贝克汉姆以“取得更多”全球销售额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-aliexpress-recruits-beckham-score-more-global-sales-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国巨头阿里巴巴旗下的电子商务网站全球速卖通 (AliExpress) 已签下前英格兰足球队长大卫·贝克汉姆 (David Beckham) 作为品牌大使，以追赶竞争对手拼多多 (PDD Holdings) 旗下的 Temu，以向更多消费者销售廉价的中国制造商品。世界。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 07:40:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-aliexpress-recruits-beckham-score-more-global-sales-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员称台湾武器即将到来，中国演习显示威慑需要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-lawmaker-says-chinas-intimidating-military-exercises-showed-no-interest-peace-2024-05-27/</link><description>一位访问台北的美国高级议员周一表示，台湾订购的武器终于在路上，中国上周的“恐吓”军事演习凸显了增强台湾威慑能力的必要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 04:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-lawmaker-says-chinas-intimidating-military-exercises-showed-no-interest-peace-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中共高级官员在瓦努阿图举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-chinese-communist-party-official-vanuatu-meetings-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国共产党高级官员刘建超周一在访问这个受到北京和美国欢迎的太平洋岛国时会见了瓦努阿图总理夏洛特·萨尔瓦伊。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 04:10:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/senior-chinese-communist-party-official-vanuatu-meetings-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>清算人完成股权出售交易后，中国恒大电动汽车部门股价飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shares-china-evergrandes-ev-unit-soar-after-liquidators-stake-sale-deal-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车集团表示，清算人已代表主要股东同意出售这家电动汽车制造商的股份，该公司周一恢复交易，该公司股价周一上涨了一倍多。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shares-china-evergrandes-ev-unit-soar-after-liquidators-stake-sale-deal-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国四川省发生5.0级地震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/earthquake-magnitude-50-hits-chinas-sichuan-province-2024-05-27/</link><description>据中国地震台网中心周一消息，中国四川省木里县发生5.0级地震。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/earthquake-magnitude-50-hits-chinas-sichuan-province-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>在中国，星巴克试图避免价格战却陷入打折潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</link><description>由于星巴克在中国的啤酒业务面临着来自快速增长、低成本竞争对手的激烈竞争，这些竞争对手已经蚕食了星巴克的市场份额，这家咖啡连锁店正越来越多地被拖入其声称希望避免的价格战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>